videos.headline: Northwestern tosses 2nd INT of 1st quarter
videos.description: Northwestern QB Aidan Smith is picked off for the second time as his pass is intercepted by UMass' Josh Wallace in the red zone.

videos.headline: Northwestern returns blocked FG for TD
videos.description: UMass attempts a 30-yard field goal, but Cooper Garcia's kick is blocked, and Chris Bergin returns it 85 yards for the Northwestern score.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Northwestern returns blocked FG for TD) 2019/11/16

videos.headline: Hull breaks free for Northwestern TD
videos.description: Northwestern RB Evan Hull breaks a tackle and scores from 38 yards out for his second touchdown of the game.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Hull breaks free for Northwestern TD) 2019/11/16

videos.headline: Northwestern's Hull finds pay dirt for 4th TD
videos.description: Northwestern RB Evan Hull adds to his career day, scoring from 31 yards out for his fourth touchdown of the game.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Northwestern's Hull finds pay dirt for 4th TD) 2019/11/16
